1
00:00:00,340 --> 00:00:02,140
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:02,210 --> 00:00:03,310
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,380 --> 00:00:05,010
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,880 --> 00:00:07,950
How dare you...

5
00:00:08,410 --> 00:00:10,780
try to replace me as chairman?

6
00:00:18,090 --> 00:00:20,390
Are you kidding me? You people!

7
00:00:20,930 --> 00:00:21,930
Darn it!

8
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,960
How dare you disrespect me?

9
00:00:27,070 --> 00:00:29,700
I was at the police station
over a misunderstanding,

10
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:32,000
and you didn't even think
of bailing me out.

11
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:34,870
Instead, you decided to betray me?

12
00:00:49,090 --> 00:00:50,090
Choi Yu Na.

13
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:53,530
Oh Jung Ran.

14
00:00:55,390 --> 00:00:58,600
Now I finally see what you're
really after, Kim Myung Hui.

15
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:03,900
How dare you try to push me out
and take my seat as chairman?

16
00:01:07,570 --> 00:01:10,140
Sir, you were taken into
emergency custody by the police.

17
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:12,540
You were dragged away
in front of the employees.

18
00:01:13,240 --> 00:01:15,350
We didn't know if it was
a misunderstanding or not.

19
00:01:15,550 --> 00:01:17,920
- To protect the Adele Group...
- Shut it!

20
00:01:18,620 --> 00:01:20,890
Even now,
you're still trying to fool me.

21
00:01:22,550 --> 00:01:24,890
I'm going to dismiss Kim Myung Hui
from her position as president,

22
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:26,760
so vote on it!

23
00:01:27,590 --> 00:01:28,590
Father.

24
00:01:28,930 --> 00:01:30,060
What are you waiting for?

25
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:32,060
Proceed with the vote immediately.

26
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,800
That's right.

27
00:01:35,630 --> 00:01:37,270
I'll dismiss Kim Myung Hui,

28
00:01:38,170 --> 00:01:39,940
and appoint Oh Jung Ran.

29
00:01:41,540 --> 00:01:42,540
Me?

30
00:01:42,970 --> 00:01:43,980
Sir.

31
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:46,780
The proposal includes
appointing Oh Jung Ran...

32
00:01:46,780 --> 00:01:47,810
as president of the bio division.

33
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:50,080
Cast your votes!

34
00:01:53,020 --> 00:01:55,220
All right. Let's vote.

35
00:02:17,410 --> 00:02:20,010
How did Chairman Park
and Park Cheol Su get released?

36
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:22,610
Oh Jung Ran and Choi Yu Na
got them out.

37
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,750
My mom?

38
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:27,750
But how? There was evidence and
they were under emergency arrest.

39
00:02:27,820 --> 00:02:30,190
How could they get them out
in less than 48 hours?

40
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,790
Who exactly did they get
to pull strings?

41
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:34,730
It seems they got
to a high-ranking police official.

42
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:38,330
Anyway, she's been the wife of the
Adele Group's chairman for 30 years.

43
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:41,200
It seems her connections
run deeper than we expected.

44
00:02:42,070 --> 00:02:44,070
My mom got in your way again.

45
00:02:46,170 --> 00:02:47,170
I'm sorry.

46
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:50,610
For now,
you should head to the office.

47
00:02:51,010 --> 00:02:52,340
As soon as Chairman Park returned,

48
00:02:52,410 --> 00:02:53,880
he dismissed
President Kim Myung Hui.

49
00:02:54,550 --> 00:02:57,520
- She was dismissed?
- Yes. What's more,

50
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:59,650
he put Oh Jung Ran in her place.

51
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:08,430
Please look into the police official
who got Chairman Park out.

52
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:11,330
I'll go to the company
and check on the situation.

53
00:03:12,930 --> 00:03:13,930
Sir!

54
00:03:15,070 --> 00:03:16,330
You're making a mistake.

55
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:18,340
You're putting Oh Jung Ran
in my place?

56
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,500
You'll regret it.

57
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:22,970
No, my mistake was trusting you.

58
00:03:24,110 --> 00:03:27,610
Not knowing you saved me
just to use me,

59
00:03:27,650 --> 00:03:29,550
I let way too much slide
just so I could trust...

60
00:03:29,550 --> 00:03:31,120
and rely on you.

61
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:34,750
Not just the president's seat,

62
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:38,260
but a marriage
and the slush fund ledger too?

63
00:03:38,620 --> 00:03:40,430
Hey, don't even dream of it.

64
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,960
So,

65
00:03:42,390 --> 00:03:44,560
you're going to trust and rely
on Oh Jung Ran now?

66
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:48,470
She tried to kill you.
Do you think that's all?

67
00:03:48,970 --> 00:03:52,040
For the past 30 years,
she's been deceiving you...

68
00:03:52,940 --> 00:03:54,070
Kim Myung Hui!

69
00:03:56,240 --> 00:04:00,180
You dared to treat me like a maid
and torment me, didn't you?

70
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:02,780
Let's see how you like it.

71
00:04:03,150 --> 00:04:04,150
Fine.

72
00:04:04,450 --> 00:04:06,320
We have a lot to talk about,
don't we?

73
00:04:06,820 --> 00:04:08,090
Bring it on.

74
00:04:08,890 --> 00:04:10,250
You...

75
00:04:10,990 --> 00:04:12,020
How dare you...

76
00:04:12,890 --> 00:04:16,160
What are you doing?
Hey, let go of me.

77
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:17,530
Where do you think you're going?

78
00:04:19,830 --> 00:04:22,100
For crying out loud.

79
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:25,970
Kim Myung Hui and Oh Jung Ran
are just the same.

80
00:04:27,310 --> 00:04:30,810
They're just trying to use me,
Park Tae Ho.

81
00:04:31,780 --> 00:04:32,780
Manager Kang!

82
00:04:34,610 --> 00:04:35,610
Yes, sir.

83
00:04:36,710 --> 00:04:41,390
Just firing Kim Myung Hui
isn't enough for me.

84
00:04:42,090 --> 00:04:43,920
Tell everyone to gather immediately.

85
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:48,290
- Everyone, including Chloe!
- Yes, sir.

86
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,800
Darn it!

87
00:05:03,410 --> 00:05:06,710
Let me go.
Why are you dragging me around?

88
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:10,010
Why? Isn't this what you wanted?

89
00:05:10,150 --> 00:05:12,350
You picked a fight on purpose
because you were afraid...

90
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:14,020
I'd reveal Hyun Jun's secret.

91
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:17,920
If you're that worried,
resign as president yourself.

92
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:22,190
For Hyun Jun's sake,
I'm giving you one last chance.

93
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:26,300
Worry about your own son
before you worry about mine.

94
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:30,940
If Hyun Jun loses his claim as heir
because his secret is revealed,

95
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:34,010
your son will lose his claim too.

96
00:05:34,110 --> 00:05:35,140
What?

97
00:05:35,210 --> 00:05:39,080
You think I came back empty-handed
after I got Park Tae Ho out?

98
00:05:40,180 --> 00:05:42,680
I've been thinking about
how to shut you up.

99
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:43,980
Park Min Jun.

100
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:48,490
You remember what he did
at Hyun Jun's wedding, don't you?

101
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,460
Using what happened that day,

102
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,820
how about I set him up?

103
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:58,500
A shameless man who had an affair
with his half-brother's wife...

104
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:00,900
What are you talking about?

105
00:06:03,230 --> 00:06:05,440
It means
things are about to get ugly.

106
00:06:05,970 --> 00:06:09,640
Hyun Jun might just get kicked out,
but your son...

107
00:06:09,940 --> 00:06:12,280
I'll make it so he can never show
his face in public again.

108
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:15,510
Oh Jung Ran, you...

109
00:06:16,210 --> 00:06:17,320
Ms. Kim!

110
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:20,080
- It's not worth it.
- Let me at her!

111
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:21,190
Please don't.

112
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:27,190
I told you when
Park Tae Ho collapsed, didn't I?

113
00:06:28,230 --> 00:06:31,200
If the two of us go to war,
we both go down together.

114
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,270
Go ahead. Mess with my Hyun Jun.

115
00:06:35,030 --> 00:06:38,270
And I'll ruin Min Jun's life too.

116
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,660
- You got my father out?
- That's right.

117
00:07:00,290 --> 00:07:03,030
Ms. Oh and I got the chairman out.

118
00:07:03,330 --> 00:07:04,530
In return, he's agreed...

119
00:07:04,730 --> 00:07:07,000
to take care of the lawsuit,

120
00:07:07,060 --> 00:07:08,930
and I'll be getting
my job back soon.

121
00:07:10,370 --> 00:07:12,970
This time, I won.

122
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,440
No.

123
00:07:14,740 --> 00:07:18,010
It won't work, no matter how much
you try to manipulate my father.

124
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:22,250
He could abandon you at any time,

125
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:23,450
and I'll...

126
00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:25,650
make sure he does.

127
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,420
We'll see about that.

128
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:32,320
You think you have
that kind of power?

129
00:07:32,820 --> 00:07:35,930
The President Kim
who protected you is gone.

130
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:39,760
And Hyun Jun could end up
becoming Adele's heir.

131
00:07:41,570 --> 00:07:42,730
Give it your best shot.

132
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,440
Just a second.

133
00:07:49,110 --> 00:07:52,010
Yes, Manager Kang. I was actually
on my way to the chairman's office.

134
00:07:52,910 --> 00:07:53,910
What?

135
00:07:54,610 --> 00:07:55,710
At the house?

136
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,180
Chloe too?

137
00:07:59,550 --> 00:08:00,590
Yes, I understand.

138
00:08:01,790 --> 00:08:03,490
Is he calling everyone to the house?

139
00:08:04,260 --> 00:08:05,260
Yes.

140
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:08,730
I'll be right there with you,
so don't worry too much.

141
00:08:20,970 --> 00:08:21,970
Right.

142
00:08:22,470 --> 00:08:26,110
If Ms. Oh can silence President Kim,

143
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:30,180
then Hyun Jun could become the heir.

144
00:08:32,250 --> 00:08:35,920
If I use Hyun Jun's weakness
to marry into the Adele family,

145
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,620
then both Hyun Jun and Adele...

146
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:42,030
will be in my hands.

147
00:08:47,230 --> 00:08:49,530
You can't let Oh Jung Ran's threats
get to you.

148
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:53,400
Just expose Hyun Jun's secret...

149
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:55,170
and take your position back.

150
00:08:55,370 --> 00:08:56,370
But...

151
00:08:58,510 --> 00:08:59,840
But what about Hyun Jun?

152
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:01,210
Sir,

153
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:04,420
this is no time to be worrying
about someone else.

154
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:08,790
Ms. Kim, are you worried
about Park Hyun Jun too?

155
00:09:09,650 --> 00:09:11,590
He's not the one I'm worried about.

156
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:15,930
It's Min Jun and Jin Ju.

157
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:19,260
If an infidelity scandal breaks
because of Oh Jung Ran's lies,

158
00:09:20,030 --> 00:09:21,770
they'll both be hurt.

159
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:26,700
Min Jun, you're worried about
Jin Ju getting hurt too, right?

160
00:09:26,940 --> 00:09:29,640
Yes. She's already
been through so much.

161
00:09:29,710 --> 00:09:31,810
I can't let her go through
something like that.

162
00:09:33,610 --> 00:09:36,480
When I learned
that Chloe was Jin Ju...

163
00:09:37,250 --> 00:09:39,480
and chose to help her
with her revenge,

164
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:41,350
I wanted...

165
00:09:42,190 --> 00:09:45,460
to make sure
she wouldn't be hurt anymore.

166
00:09:47,890 --> 00:09:50,330
Maybe I feel guilty,

167
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:52,630
or maybe I just feel responsible.

168
00:10:04,110 --> 00:10:06,710
The chairman has called
a family meeting.

169
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:25,460
As expected, you always
come through with a reward.

170
00:10:26,330 --> 00:10:28,830
I won't let you down
as president of the bio division.

171
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:31,640
But...

172
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,470
are you only going
to dismiss Kim Myung Hui...

173
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:36,470
and do nothing about Park Min Jun?

174
00:10:37,210 --> 00:10:39,680
Since I'll be president,
wouldn't Hyun Jun...

175
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:42,180
be a better fit
for the vice president position?

176
00:10:55,330 --> 00:10:58,160
Sir, I'm glad to see you're out.

177
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:08,170
I'm so relieved.

178
00:11:12,380 --> 00:11:13,380
You're relieved?

179
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:16,910
You found Park Cheol Su
and reported me to the police,

180
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:19,250
and you have the nerve
to say you're relieved?

181
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,020
Please, don't do this.

182
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:24,820
Did you know about this?

183
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:27,390
Were you aware
that this thing conspired...

184
00:11:27,690 --> 00:11:29,830
with Kim Myung Hui and reported me?

185
00:11:29,930 --> 00:11:34,200
You know that Ms. Kim and Chloe
don't get along.

186
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:37,900
Exactly.
Hyun Jun didn't know about it.

187
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:43,210
You pathetic fool. You were right
beside her and couldn't even tell?

188
00:11:43,610 --> 00:11:46,610
You're actually buying
that disgusting act of hers?

189
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:48,980
I think you've got the wrong idea...

190
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:51,220
because Chloe had been searching
for Park Cheol Su.

191
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:54,550
Mom, tell him.
You're the one who ordered it.

192
00:11:55,290 --> 00:11:57,420
Yes, Mother, please tell him.

193
00:11:58,060 --> 00:12:01,990
What are you talking about?
Kim Myung Hui was behind it all.

194
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:08,000
Don't try to drag me into this.
Just beg the chairman to spare you.

195
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:10,800
Manager Kang!

196
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,200
Yes, sir.

197
00:12:15,140 --> 00:12:18,940
Throw this thing
out of my house right now.

198
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,950
If Chloe leaves,

199
00:12:21,950 --> 00:12:23,080
I'm leaving too.

200
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:26,750
Hyun Jun, read the room, would you?

201
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:31,590
Fine. If you've decided
you don't want to be my son,

202
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:33,190
then both of you get out.

203
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,930
Are you really okay with this?

204
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:39,960
Even if I'm not your son?

205
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:42,130
Does it really not matter to you?

206
00:12:42,130 --> 00:12:43,200
Hyun Jun!

207
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:09,790
Seeing as Chairman Park
told everyone to gather,

208
00:13:10,330 --> 00:13:12,000
it seems like something's
about to happen.

209
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:20,970
Jung Ran, Hyun Jun, and even Chloe.
Will everyone be okay?

210
00:13:23,070 --> 00:13:27,440
What if Ms. Kim gets cornered
and reveals Hyun Jun's secret?

211
00:13:29,180 --> 00:13:30,180
No.

212
00:13:31,780 --> 00:13:33,180
That can't happen.

213
00:13:41,190 --> 00:13:42,230
Manager Kang.

214
00:13:42,730 --> 00:13:44,500
Vice President Park Min Jun...

215
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:46,830
will be demoted back to director.

216
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:49,530
Sir.

217
00:13:52,970 --> 00:13:55,770
If you suspect me,
then take it out on me.

218
00:13:56,010 --> 00:13:58,610
- Leave Min Jun out of this.
- Park Hyun Jun.

219
00:13:59,380 --> 00:14:03,080
Promise me, right here,
that you'll break up with Chloe.

220
00:14:03,180 --> 00:14:06,380
If you do,
I'll make you vice president...

221
00:14:06,420 --> 00:14:09,650
and put you in line
to inherit Adele Group.

222
00:14:12,190 --> 00:14:14,120
Say you'll do it. Now.

223
00:14:14,230 --> 00:14:15,260
I don't want it.

224
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:16,260
What?

225
00:14:16,260 --> 00:14:18,100
I'll never leave Chloe.

226
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:20,500
Sir, if our marriage is annulled,

227
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:22,300
the exclusive development rights project
will also...

228
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:25,040
I'll just pay the penalty!

229
00:14:25,800 --> 00:14:28,810
End things with my son
and get out now.

230
00:14:35,010 --> 00:14:37,480
Since you're so upset, sir,

231
00:14:38,020 --> 00:14:40,180
I'll leave for now.

232
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:42,920
Chloe?

233
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:48,490
But we will stay married.

234
00:14:48,890 --> 00:14:51,560
Once the JKL Partners legal team
steps in...

235
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:53,560
and the penalty is assessed,

236
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,670
you'll change your mind.

237
00:14:55,700 --> 00:14:57,770
I'll come back then.

238
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:11,220
And Kim Myung Hui, you get out too.

239
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,320
Father.

240
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:17,890
Oh Jung Ran will stay in
the main house. And Kim Myung Hui...

241
00:15:18,390 --> 00:15:19,960
will move to the annex.

242
00:15:20,020 --> 00:15:21,490
Wait, really?

243
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:25,930
Kim Myung Hui is out as president
and out of the main house?

244
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:28,600
And Park Min Jun is out
as vice president too?

245
00:15:29,430 --> 00:15:32,470
Does that mean Hyun Jun and I will
be president and vice president?

246
00:15:32,900 --> 00:15:35,740
That's only if Hyun Jun
breaks up with Chloe.

247
00:15:36,170 --> 00:15:37,470
Bring me his answer first.

248
00:15:38,110 --> 00:15:39,440
Unbelievable.

249
00:15:40,540 --> 00:15:41,650
Darn it.

250
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:44,750
Sir.

251
00:15:46,020 --> 00:15:47,150
Don't bother me!

252
00:16:11,540 --> 00:16:13,240
I need to recover quickly.

253
00:16:14,550 --> 00:16:17,720
I have to crush those
who betrayed me.

254
00:16:18,780 --> 00:16:22,020
I'll make them pay
for underestimating me,

255
00:16:22,820 --> 00:16:24,560
for every bit of it.

256
00:16:33,900 --> 00:16:37,570
I've packed only the essentials
you'll need right away.

257
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:40,440
President Kim,
please go to the annex.

258
00:16:41,110 --> 00:16:42,870
Ms. Chloe, please leave.

259
00:16:46,110 --> 00:16:47,180
Not now.

260
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:51,720
Right.

261
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:54,280
It's time to walk on eggshells
around the chairman.

262
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:57,650
Hurry up and get out.

263
00:17:01,490 --> 00:17:02,930
Don't get too excited.

264
00:17:03,690 --> 00:17:06,760
If I change my mind
and decide to play dirty,

265
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,770
this whole situation could change
in an instant.

266
00:17:20,210 --> 00:17:22,580
By the way, you two,

267
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:25,380
what's the real story here?

268
00:17:26,250 --> 00:17:28,550
Like the chairman said,
did you two conspire...

269
00:17:29,050 --> 00:17:30,490
and report him?

270
00:17:38,560 --> 00:17:39,830
How could you?

271
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:43,330
I only searched for Park Cheol Su
because you told me to.

272
00:17:43,700 --> 00:17:46,240
You didn't even tell the chairman
it was a misunderstanding.

273
00:17:46,670 --> 00:17:50,240
And now you're framing me
by tying me to Ms. Kim?

274
00:17:51,740 --> 00:17:56,550
I truly regret ever looking
for Park Cheol Su for you.

275
00:18:00,150 --> 00:18:01,150
Chloe!

276
00:18:03,150 --> 00:18:04,460
Mom, honestly!

277
00:18:06,020 --> 00:18:07,020
Where do you think you're going?

278
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:08,560
Do as your father said
and end things.

279
00:18:09,790 --> 00:18:11,900
Then you'll be vice president
and the successor.

280
00:18:14,330 --> 00:18:15,600
- Hyun Jun.
- Chloe.

281
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:16,730
Park Hyun Jun!

282
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:21,370
Let me help you with that.

283
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:24,170
I'll do it.

284
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:26,810
It's all right.

285
00:18:27,780 --> 00:18:29,310
You hurry upstairs.

286
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:31,820
Don't clash with your father.

287
00:18:32,380 --> 00:18:34,180
Just hold your ground
and protect your position.

288
00:18:35,220 --> 00:18:37,290
We'll wait for the storm to pass...

289
00:18:37,820 --> 00:18:39,460
and wait for another opening.

290
00:18:58,980 --> 00:19:00,780
Just give me a few days.

291
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,650
I'll use the exclusive
development rights...

292
00:19:02,710 --> 00:19:03,880
to persuade my father again.

293
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:05,750
Don't push it.

294
00:19:06,650 --> 00:19:09,790
Clashing with Chairman Park now
will only backfire.

295
00:19:10,590 --> 00:19:12,460
That's why I'm keeping
my distance, too.

296
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:16,830
I need to watch how things play out
and figure out my next move.

297
00:19:18,730 --> 00:19:22,570
Will our marriage be
one of the things you consider?

298
00:19:24,230 --> 00:19:25,700
You're not thinking about...

299
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:29,010
ending our marriage
like my father suggested, are you?

300
00:19:31,810 --> 00:19:33,680
Maybe I should move in here.

301
00:19:34,040 --> 00:19:36,610
No. Let's register
our marriage first.

302
00:19:36,710 --> 00:19:39,450
We need to make it official.

303
00:19:39,820 --> 00:19:41,690
Let me think about it.

304
00:19:43,220 --> 00:19:44,520
You should go now.

305
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:47,520
Sure.

306
00:19:58,770 --> 00:19:59,770
I'm sorry.

307
00:20:01,510 --> 00:20:05,440
I'm sorry that my mom is interfering
and making this so hard...

308
00:20:09,710 --> 00:20:11,010
and that I'm Park Tae Ho's son.

309
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:13,720
I'm sorry.

310
00:20:15,790 --> 00:20:20,090
I was going to tell you
about President Kim.

311
00:20:21,120 --> 00:20:23,390
That she's going to be
the next chairman,

312
00:20:23,460 --> 00:20:25,730
so you can stop fighting over
the succession.

313
00:20:26,430 --> 00:20:29,300
That it's okay even if you're not
Chairman Park's son.

314
00:20:29,670 --> 00:20:32,870
That you don't have to suffer
because of that secret.

315
00:20:34,710 --> 00:20:36,540
I really wanted to tell you that.

316
00:20:37,670 --> 00:20:39,840
But what do I do now?

317
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:42,480
What should I do?

318
00:21:03,630 --> 00:21:05,440
I'll just have to start over.

319
00:21:07,470 --> 00:21:09,070
Instead of going
through Park Tae Ho,

320
00:21:09,740 --> 00:21:11,910
I'll take down Oh Jung Ran myself...

321
00:21:14,140 --> 00:21:15,880
and reclaim my position.

322
00:21:29,630 --> 00:21:30,690
Dad.

323
00:21:31,800 --> 00:21:32,830
Chairman Park...

324
00:21:33,460 --> 00:21:35,930
beat the system and got out again.

325
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:39,370
The same way
he covered up your accident,

326
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:41,510
he bends the law to his will.

327
00:21:43,340 --> 00:21:45,340
Kim Myung Hui, who helped us...

328
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:46,840
I mean,

329
00:21:47,910 --> 00:21:50,350
even President Kim Dan Hui
has been hurt by this,

330
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:54,020
so how can I help her?

331
00:21:57,820 --> 00:22:01,290
Dad, please show me the way.

332
00:22:01,690 --> 00:22:02,690
(Hanbit High School
62nd Graduation Ceremony)

333
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:17,740
You still have
the P.O. box key, right?

334
00:22:18,110 --> 00:22:20,680
Of course. I always have it with me.

335
00:22:21,710 --> 00:22:24,650
Good. In a few days,
an important item...

336
00:22:32,460 --> 00:22:34,120
To access the P.O. box,

337
00:22:35,830 --> 00:22:37,830
I have to be Baek Jin Ju.

338
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:41,530
Will the day ever come...

339
00:22:42,300 --> 00:22:46,140
when I can reclaim my name
and open the P.O. box?

340
00:23:00,220 --> 00:23:01,220
Darn!

341
00:23:01,690 --> 00:23:03,120
After all the trouble
we went through...

342
00:23:03,190 --> 00:23:04,550
to lock up Park Cheol Su
and Park Tae Ho?

343
00:23:05,890 --> 00:23:08,160
Oh Jung Ran and Choi Yu Na
were one step ahead of us.

344
00:23:08,930 --> 00:23:09,930
Tell me about it.

345
00:23:10,190 --> 00:23:11,530
If only they'd arrived
an hour later...

346
00:23:11,530 --> 00:23:13,900
No, even 30 minutes later.

347
00:23:14,830 --> 00:23:17,900
None of this would've happened
if Dan Hui had been appointed chairman.

348
00:23:19,040 --> 00:23:20,440
To think she lost her position
as president...

349
00:23:20,970 --> 00:23:22,340
and was kicked out to the annex.

350
00:23:22,740 --> 00:23:25,840
Shoot, after everything
we've endured to get here?

351
00:23:27,910 --> 00:23:28,910
I'm sorry.

352
00:23:29,610 --> 00:23:32,180
You helped Jin Ju,
and this is how things turned out.

353
00:23:34,750 --> 00:23:35,750
Please don't say that.

354
00:23:36,250 --> 00:23:38,690
It was something
I had to do for Dr. Baek.

355
00:23:38,790 --> 00:23:39,790
That's right.

356
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:42,590
The only ones who should be sorry
are Oh Jung Ran and Choi Yu Na.

357
00:23:43,330 --> 00:23:45,400
So, did you look into it?

358
00:23:45,760 --> 00:23:48,930
Who let Chairman Park
and Park Cheol Su walk free?

359
00:23:49,370 --> 00:23:51,000
- Seriously.
- Right, yes.

360
00:23:51,270 --> 00:23:53,340
As a matter of fact,
I received a photo.

361
00:23:53,870 --> 00:23:54,940
You did?

362
00:23:55,170 --> 00:23:58,610
I'll go break his nose if I have to.
Let me see.

363
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,480
Here.

364
00:24:03,750 --> 00:24:04,750
What?

365
00:24:05,750 --> 00:24:07,250
Isn't he...

366
00:24:10,590 --> 00:24:13,120
What is it? Do you both know him?

367
00:24:26,770 --> 00:24:29,340
It's been a while, Detective Yun.

368
00:24:31,840 --> 00:24:33,640
I'm not a detective anymore.

369
00:24:34,440 --> 00:24:36,550
Just like you went
from president to chairman,

370
00:24:36,810 --> 00:24:38,780
I'm the Deputy Chief of Police now.

371
00:24:42,690 --> 00:24:45,720
The evidence against you
was solid this time,

372
00:24:46,560 --> 00:24:48,330
so it took some effort
to clean things up.

373
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:52,130
If it weren't for me, you wouldn't
have gotten out so easily.

374
00:24:54,730 --> 00:24:58,340
I did this for Adele Group,
not for the money.

375
00:24:59,900 --> 00:25:03,670
So show me what Adele Group
is truly capable of.

376
00:25:05,180 --> 00:25:07,280
Sure. I'll do that.

377
00:25:20,060 --> 00:25:21,060
That punk.

378
00:25:21,990 --> 00:25:24,430
He got in our way 30 years ago,
and he's still at it.

379
00:25:27,560 --> 00:25:29,330
Since he's a high-ranking
police official,

380
00:25:29,600 --> 00:25:31,470
the investigation
will be much harder.

381
00:25:32,370 --> 00:25:33,770
Still, we have to try.

382
00:25:33,770 --> 00:25:36,070
The intel team will keep searching
for Park Cheol Su.

383
00:25:36,770 --> 00:25:38,740
Next time, we just need
to be better prepared...

384
00:25:38,810 --> 00:25:39,810
so he can't get involved.

385
00:25:40,210 --> 00:25:41,750
The problem is Dan Hui.

386
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:44,450
How is this happening
all over again after seven years?

387
00:25:45,350 --> 00:25:47,750
We thought it'd be game over
once we got Dr. Baek's evidence,

388
00:25:48,020 --> 00:25:49,190
but look what happened.

389
00:25:49,250 --> 00:25:51,720
Just when we thought we'd finally
gotten justice for Myung Hui,

390
00:25:51,890 --> 00:25:52,890
everything fell apart again.

391
00:25:53,820 --> 00:25:55,990
Wait. Hold on.

392
00:25:56,330 --> 00:25:58,760
Dr. Baek's evidence
from seven years ago?

393
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:02,930
He told me
he'd give me evidence proving...

394
00:26:03,330 --> 00:26:04,870
Oh Jung Ran is a murderer.

395
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:13,640
Back then, Dr. Baek said...

396
00:26:14,140 --> 00:26:16,650
the evidence had arrived
from the US.

397
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:20,350
Don't tell me the evidence
you're talking about is...

398
00:26:21,320 --> 00:26:22,320
the pearl.

399
00:26:23,320 --> 00:26:24,490
The bloodstained pearl?

400
00:26:25,360 --> 00:26:26,390
How did you know?

401
00:26:27,190 --> 00:26:30,660
Dr. Baek contacted me,
and I sent it to Korea.

402
00:26:31,190 --> 00:26:33,700
So the evidence is in Korea?

403
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:37,200
He clearly said he'd receive it
at his daughter's P.O. box.

404
00:26:40,070 --> 00:26:41,070
I'm here.

405
00:26:55,950 --> 00:26:57,250
What's going on?

406
00:27:00,920 --> 00:27:02,330
Are you kidding me?

407
00:27:02,330 --> 00:27:04,560
What do you mean
you can't open the P.O. box?

408
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:07,100
Who are you to keep us...

409
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:09,530
from getting the evidence
Dr. Baek promised?

410
00:27:09,570 --> 00:27:12,200
I'm against this
as Jin Ju's guardian.

411
00:27:12,300 --> 00:27:15,370
It's not like opening the P.O. Box
will hurt Jin Ju.

412
00:27:15,370 --> 00:27:17,040
Because she has to become
Baek Jin Ju!

413
00:27:17,040 --> 00:27:19,280
But she already is Baek Jin Ju!

414
00:27:30,720 --> 00:27:31,960
You have to be Jin Ju...

415
00:27:32,990 --> 00:27:34,790
to access it, not Chloe.

416
00:27:35,730 --> 00:27:36,730
Yes.

417
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:39,800
Identity verification is mandatory
for that company's P.O. boxes.

418
00:27:40,060 --> 00:27:42,100
Only she can access the box.

419
00:27:42,370 --> 00:27:44,200
If there's any record
of her entering,

420
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:45,670
it'll prove she's alive.

421
00:27:46,270 --> 00:27:49,140
I'm sorry, but I can't put Jin Ju...

422
00:27:49,570 --> 00:27:51,110
in danger.

423
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:53,340
There's no way I'm doing that.

424
00:27:54,610 --> 00:27:56,510
Well, if that's the reason,

425
00:27:57,250 --> 00:27:58,920
we can't keep insisting
that you open it.

426
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:22,310
Jin Ju,

427
00:28:24,770 --> 00:28:26,280
your safety is more important...

428
00:28:27,340 --> 00:28:28,680
than President Kim Myung Hui.

429
00:28:29,710 --> 00:28:33,080
But this happened to her
while she was helping us.

430
00:28:33,620 --> 00:28:35,950
You said Chairman Park suspects you
and is watching you.

431
00:28:36,390 --> 00:28:39,320
If you open the P.O. box
and Chairman Park finds out,

432
00:28:39,690 --> 00:28:41,390
he'll do whatever it takes
to kill you again.

433
00:28:42,290 --> 00:28:43,330
I know you're grateful
to President Kim...

434
00:28:43,330 --> 00:28:44,330
and feel bad for her,

435
00:28:44,660 --> 00:28:46,460
but revealing your identity
as Baek Jin Ju...

436
00:28:46,760 --> 00:28:47,760
is extremely dangerous.

437
00:29:04,080 --> 00:29:05,520
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

438
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:07,920
What the heck?

439
00:29:08,420 --> 00:29:09,990
All our things are...

440
00:29:12,090 --> 00:29:14,760
Serves you right
for not clearing out sooner.

441
00:29:18,530 --> 00:29:22,300
Now that you've been fired,
you should've cleaned out your desk.

442
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:27,840
Looks like you're sucking up
to Oh Jung Ran now.

443
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:31,440
I don't know. Even without trying,

444
00:29:32,810 --> 00:29:33,980
we're getting along just fine.

445
00:29:33,980 --> 00:29:35,710
Hasn't reality sunk in yet
just because...

446
00:29:36,280 --> 00:29:37,810
you haven't been kicked out
of the house?

447
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:41,080
You're finished at Adele Group.

448
00:29:42,190 --> 00:29:44,020
Take your things and get lost.

449
00:29:52,100 --> 00:29:53,500
I can't believe them!

450
00:30:08,580 --> 00:30:10,980
(Special Award)

451
00:30:26,730 --> 00:30:27,730
How did you...

452
00:30:28,700 --> 00:30:31,600
I felt like I had to finish
what I started.

453
00:30:33,300 --> 00:30:34,300
Finish what?

454
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:35,910
The task...

455
00:30:37,840 --> 00:30:39,610
my father left me seven years ago.

456
00:31:12,410 --> 00:31:14,740
This is the evidence
my father tried...

457
00:31:15,380 --> 00:31:17,650
to give you seven years ago.

458
00:31:19,320 --> 00:31:20,380
Right.

459
00:31:21,420 --> 00:31:23,320
This was the evidence
that Dr. Baek found...

460
00:31:24,620 --> 00:31:26,420
and protected.

461
00:31:26,990 --> 00:31:28,320
I'm finally giving you...

462
00:31:30,160 --> 00:31:31,530
what my father wanted you to have.

463
00:31:33,060 --> 00:31:35,160
I'm sorry for making you take...

464
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:37,400
such a big risk.

465
00:31:38,870 --> 00:31:40,400
You lost your position
as president...

466
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:42,340
because you helped me.

467
00:31:44,870 --> 00:31:46,940
Use this to get your revenge...

468
00:31:47,580 --> 00:31:49,110
and reclaim your position.

469
00:32:48,810 --> 00:32:51,710
(Pearl in Red)

470
00:32:51,910 --> 00:32:53,780
Chairman Park will continue
to be suspicious.

471
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:55,040
Are you sure you'll be okay?

472
00:32:55,140 --> 00:32:57,850
I have no reason to be afraid
of his suspicions anymore.

473
00:32:57,980 --> 00:33:01,250
In fact, I'm going to make him
even more suspicious of me.

474
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:04,250
Now that Park Tae Ho is
suspicious of Kim Myung Hui,

475
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:06,090
this is my chance to strike.

476
00:33:06,360 --> 00:33:08,320
This is my opportunity
to prove myself.

477
00:33:08,690 --> 00:33:10,460
What? The nation's plagiarist?

478
00:33:10,460 --> 00:33:12,200
Before you ruin everything,

479
00:33:12,330 --> 00:33:14,100
I'll save myself,

480
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:16,330
even if it means marrying
into the Adele family.

481
00:33:17,270 --> 00:33:19,270
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
